### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Créer une notification pour un utilisateur (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/create-notification
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "type": "info",
  "title": "Nouvelle information",
  "message": "Votre événement a été mis à jour"
}

### Test 2 - Créer une notification globale (pour tous les admins)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/create-notification
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": null,
  "type": "system",
  "title": "Maintenance programmée",
  "message": "Une maintenance est prévue ce soir à 22h"
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: type manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/create-notification
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "title": "Titre",
  "message": "Message"
}

### Test 4 - Erreur: title manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/create-notification
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "type": "info",
  "message": "Message"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: accès non autorisé (client)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/create-notification
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "type": "info",
  "title": "Titre",
  "message": "Message"
}

